

A fully autnonomous artificial animal. This plugin provides a plug-and-play brain that can be added to any Actor and to simulate real-life entities. It is fully transparent, indefinately extensible and made to work offline and autonomous. Targeting mobile devices as deployable brain. It is not meant to be the smartest intelligence, but to capture regular animal social behavior and intelligence. In other words, it simulates animals. Opposed to big companies, it is yours and will remein yours.

And functionality should increase in the future. We could even combine measurements of brains in real-time, as we have experience with that, but we don't see a direct application for now.




Current Features:

- Object Recognition

- Face Recognition

- Speech Recognition (Speech-to-Text and Speaker Recognition)

- Social Awareness (Parents, Relatives and others)

- Spatial Awareness (Depth Recognition and Imagined Environment and Objects)

- Control and Sensoring

- Emotions (basic)

- Memory




- Higher Cognition Module (Optional use of Large Language and Visual Language Models)





Other Features:

- Blueprint and visual-based Development

- Increasing support for platform-based hardware (Android, Arduino)

- Priority on affordable and widely available Platforms




