Disclaimer

Many things are still rudimentary, due to the very complexity of underlying concepts. It is also not the aim to create the most intelligent agents, but to recreate behavior and emotions on the most basic level and to have precisely educative aspects by building from the ground up concepts in the simplest possible manner.

Updates to the newest Unreal version might come delayed, as third party plugins and hardware interfaces need to be updated too.

The high price for the professional version is to prevent big companies from simply copying the code.




